WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.136 --> 00:00:04.938
Oh... West-South Peak. 

00:00:05.105 --> 00:00:06.139
Oh My God.

00:00:06.339 --> 00:00:07.941
It was not easy 900m

00:00:08.942 --> 00:00:10.443
and 1.5 hour.

00:00:10.910 --> 00:00:14.614
TAIWAN  has 285 peaks over 3000 meters.

00:00:14.948 --> 00:00:16.683
Most hikers know the famous Baiyue

00:00:16.816 --> 00:00:18.084
The hundred peaks.

00:00:18.251 --> 00:00:20.787
But there are many more
that just few people climb.

00:00:21.054 --> 00:00:21.721
My goal:

00:00:21.855 --> 00:00:24.257
climb all seven peaks of Baigu in one push.

00:00:25.091 --> 00:00:26.192
Round 2

00:00:26.526 --> 00:00:27.694
The Bamboo Battle

00:00:28.428 --> 00:00:29.596
I detoured south

00:00:29.729 --> 00:00:31.898
to West-South Peak of Baigu Mountain.

00:00:32.465 --> 00:00:34.467
On the map, just 900 meters,

00:00:34.567 --> 00:00:36.169
but it took me 1.5 hours

00:00:36.336 --> 00:00:38.138
in one direction and then back.

00:00:39.406 --> 00:00:42.809
Incredibly dense bamboo, not much marking.

00:00:43.376 --> 00:00:45.111
You may notice my fancy goggles,

00:00:45.111 --> 00:00:47.881
last what you need here is poked eye.

00:00:51.251 --> 00:00:53.053
I was thinking about the purpose of life

00:00:53.219 --> 00:00:54.854
while pushing through that bamboo.

